snippet.title: Demon Compass — The Game (Trailer)
snippet.description:
Our game DEMON COMPASS is now available for download on Steam + physical copies of the game and other game related merch has been added to the online store — https://shop.provoker.zone

A game by - Provoker & @xenaspectrale
Produced by - Spawn Kill Studios
Creative Directors - Christian Petty, Jonathon Lopez Story Concepts - Christian Petty, Jonathon Lopez, @jk_louie

Game Development - Xena-Spectrale
Level Design - Xena-Spectrale
3D Art, Animations & 2D Textures - Xena-Spectrale Additional 2D Art - @zhecon_
Cover Artwork, UI & Manual Design - @williamjcanning
